Incident response template

Field	Details /             Instructions
Report ID:	                IR-0001
Date/Time of Incident:    	DD/MM/YYYY HH:MM
Reported By:               	Name & Position
Location:	                  Physical or virtual location of the incident
Incident Description:     	Detailed narrative of the incident, including sequence of events and how it was detected
Impact Assessment:	        List affected systems, severity (Low/Medium/High), and potential business/data impact
Immediate Actions Taken:	  Steps to contain or mitigate the incident (e.g., disconnecting systems, notifying security teams)
Root Cause Analysis:Optional: Identify the cause (e.g., phishing email, malware, misconfiguration)
Recovery Plan:	            Steps taken to restore affected systems and resume normal operations
Recommendations / Preventive Measures:	Actions to prevent future incidents (e.g., training, patching, policy updates)
Reported To:	              Supervisor / Manager / Security Officer
 Signature:               	___________________

